title: Rory Jennings (rugby union)
text: Rory Jennings (born 24 December 1995 in <a href="Oxford">Oxford</a>, <a href="England">England</a>) is an English professional <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> footballer. He plays at <a href="fly%20half">fly half</a> for English club <a href="London%20Irish">London Irish</a> in <a href="Premiership%20Rugby">Premiership Rugby</a>. He previously played for English sides <a href="Coventry%20RFC">Coventry</a> and <a href="Bath%20Rugby">Bath</a> and French club <a href="ASM%20Clermont%20Auvergne">Clermont Auvergne.</a>
